The paper focuses on face anti-spoofing, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves designing a CNN model with a novel loss function and a domain adaptation component, which are both related to machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves experiments and evaluations, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper deals with security and authentication, which could be categorized under cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques, which could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
